sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Llama Stack Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as Inline Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant Remote as Remote Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as KFP API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Garak as Garak Subprocess<br/>(local CLI)
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 / MinIO<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Safety as Llama Stack Safety API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Files as Llama Stack Files API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant EvalHub as Eval-Hub Job<br/>(K8s Pod)
    participant EHAdapter as GarakAdapter<br/>(in-process)

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,Files: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation (Llama Stack Provider)
        Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_benchmark<br/>Auth: None (cluster-internal)
        LLS->>Inline: invoke GarakInlineEvalAdapter
        Inline->>Garak: spawn subprocess<br/>(process group isolation)
        Garak->>vLLM: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        vLLM-->>Garak: Model response
        Garak-->>Inline: Scan results (JSONL)
        Inline->>Safety: POST /safety/run_shield<br/>Input/output guardrails
        Safety-->>Inline: Shield scan result
        Inline->>Files: POST /files/upload<br/>Reports & artifacts
        Files-->>Inline: File ID
        Inline-->>LLS: Evaluation result
        LLS-->>Client: Benchmark result + file references
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,Files: Flow 2: Remote KFP Evaluation (Llama Stack Provider)
        Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_benchmark<br/>Auth: None (cluster-internal)
        LLS->>Remote: invoke GarakRemoteEvalAdapter
        Remote->>KFP: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / SA
        KFP-->>Remote: Pipeline run ID
        Note over KFP,KFPPod: 6-step KFP pipeline executes
        KFPPod->>Files: GET /files/download<br/>Fetch config artifacts
        Files-->>KFPPod: Benchmark config
        KFPPod->>vLLM: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (from Secret)
        vLLM-->>KFPPod: Model responses
        KFPPod->>Files: POST /files/upload<br/>Scan results & reports
        Files-->>KFPPod: File IDs
        Remote->>KFP: GET /apis/v2beta1/runs/{id}<br/>Poll for completion
        KFP-->>Remote: Run status: completed
        Remote-->>LLS: Evaluation result
        LLS-->>Client: Benchmark result + file references
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over EvalHub,S3: Flow 3: Eval-Hub KFP Evaluation
        EvalHub->>EHAdapter: run_benchmark_job()
        EHAdapter->>KFP: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        KFP-->>EHAdapter: Pipeline run ID
        Note over KFP,KFPPod: 6-step KFP pipeline executes
        KFPPod->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (Data Connection)
        S3-->>KFPPod: Upload confirmed
        KFPPod->>vLLM: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: API Key (from /mnt/model-auth)
        vLLM-->>KFPPod: Model responses
        KFPPod->>S3: PUT scan results<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
        S3-->>KFPPod: Upload confirmed
        EHAdapter->>KFP: GET /apis/v2beta1/runs/{id}<br/>Poll for completion
        KFP-->>EHAdapter: Run status: completed
        EHAdapter->>S3: GET scan results<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
        S3-->>EHAdapter: Scan artifacts
        EHAdapter-->>EvalHub: Evaluation metrics + artifacts
    end
